{
  "video_id": "xPTmHKlH7s4",
  "title": "Andrew Bastawrous: Get your next eye exam on a smartphone",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13542.0,
      "end_time": 16386.0,
      "text": "There are 39 million people in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16386.0,
      "end_time": 17875.0,
      "text": "who are blind."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17876.0,
      "end_time": 20350.0,
      "text": "Eighty percent of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20350.0,
      "end_time": 23169.0,
      "text": "are living in low-income countries such as Kenya,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23169.0,
      "end_time": 25118.0,
      "text": "and the absolute majority"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25118.0,
      "end_time": 26625.0,
      "text": "do not need to be blind."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26625.0,
      "end_time": 28480.0,
      "text": "They are blind from diseases"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28480.0,
      "end_time": 32256.0,
      "text": "that are either completely curable or preventable."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32256.0,
      "end_time": 34768.0,
      "text": "Knowing this, with my young family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34768.0,
      "end_time": 36162.0,
      "text": "we moved to Kenya."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36162.0,
      "end_time": 37969.0,
      "text": "We secured equipment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37969.0,
      "end_time": 41668.0,
      "text": "funds, vehicles, we trained a team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41668.0,
      "end_time": 43692.0,
      "text": "we set up a hundred clinics throughout"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43692.0,
      "end_time": 45190.0,
      "text": "the Great Rift Valley"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 45190.0,
      "end_time": 48650.0,
      "text": "to try and understand a single question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48651.0,
      "end_time": 50737.0,
      "text": "why are people going blind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50737.0,
      "end_time": 53656.0,
      "text": "and what can we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53656.0,
      "end_time": 56570.0,
      "text": "The challenges were great."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56570.0,
      "end_time": 58401.0,
      "text": "When we got to where we were going,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58401.0,
      "end_time": 61670.0,
      "text": "we set up our high-tech equipment."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61670.0,
      "end_time": 63246.0,
      "text": "Power was rarely available."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63246.0,
      "end_time": 64990.0,
      "text": "We&#39;d have to run our equipment"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 64989.99999999999,
      "end_time": 66999.0,
      "text": "from petrol power generators."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 66999.0,
      "end_time": 68946.0,
      "text": "And then something occurred to me:"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 68946.0,
      "end_time": 71441.0,
      "text": "There has to be an easier way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 71441.0,
      "end_time": 73441.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s the patients who are the most in need"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 73441.0,
      "end_time": 74999.0,
      "text": "of access to eye care"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 74999.0,
      "end_time": 77339.0,
      "text": "who are the least likely to get it."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 77340.0,
      "end_time": 78446.0,
      "text": "More people in Kenya,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 78446.0,
      "end_time": 80358.0,
      "text": "and in sub-Saharan Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 80358.0,
      "end_time": 82149.0,
      "text": "have access to a mobile phone"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 82149.0,
      "end_time": 84302.0,
      "text": "than they do clean running water."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 84302.0,
      "end_time": 86210.0,
      "text": "So we said, could we harness"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 86210.0,
      "end_time": 87640.0,
      "text": "the power of mobile technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 87640.0,
      "end_time": 89791.0,
      "text": "to deliver eye care in a new way?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 89791.0,
      "end_time": 91576.0,
      "text": "And so we developed Peek,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 91576.0,
      "end_time": 94113.0,
      "text": "a smartphone [system] that enables"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 94114.0,
      "end_time": 95626.0,
      "text": "community healthcare workers"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 95626.0,
      "end_time": 99456.0,
      "text": "and empowers them to deliver eye care everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 99456.0,
      "end_time": 102126.0,
      "text": "We set about replacing traditional hospital equipment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 102126.0,
      "end_time": 104649.0,
      "text": "which is bulky, expensive and fragile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 104649.0,
      "end_time": 106684.0,
      "text": "with smartphone apps and hardware"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 106684.0,
      "end_time": 108821.0,
      "text": "that make it possible to test anyone"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 108821.0,
      "end_time": 112900.0,
      "text": "in any language and of any age."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 112100.0,
      "end_time": 113814.0,
      "text": "Here we have a demonstration"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 113814.0,
      "end_time": 115536.0,
      "text": "of a three-month-old having their vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 115537.0,
      "end_time": 119910.0,
      "text": "accurately tested using an app and an eye tracker."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 123650.0,
      "end_time": 125393.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve got many trials going on"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 125393.0,
      "end_time": 127593.0,
      "text": "in the community and in schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 127593.0,
      "end_time": 129493.0,
      "text": "and through the lessons that we&#39;ve learned in the field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 129493.0,
      "end_time": 131196.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve realized it&#39;s extremely important"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 131196.0,
      "end_time": 134560.0,
      "text": "to share the data in non-medical jargon"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 134560.0,
      "end_time": 135717.0,
      "text": "so that people understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 135717.0,
      "end_time": 138340.0,
      "text": "what we&#39;re examining and what that means to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 138340.0,
      "end_time": 139614.0,
      "text": "So here, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 139614.0,
      "end_time": 141470.0,
      "text": "we use our sight sim application,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 141470.0,
      "end_time": 143262.0,
      "text": "once your vision has been measured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 143262.0,
      "end_time": 145972.0,
      "text": "to show carers and teachers"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 145972.0,
      "end_time": 148486.0,
      "text": "what the visual world is like for that person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 148486.0,
      "end_time": 151952.0,
      "text": "so they can empathize with them and help them."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 151952.0,
      "end_time": 154340.0,
      "text": "Once we&#39;ve discovered somebody has low vision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 154340.0,
      "end_time": 156911.0,
      "text": "the next big challenge is to work out why,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 156911.0,
      "end_time": 158280.0,
      "text": "and to be able to do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 158280.0,
      "end_time": 160529.0,
      "text": "we need to have access to the inside of the eye."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 160529.0,
      "end_time": 163115.0,
      "text": "Traditionally, this requires expensive equipment"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 163115.0,
      "end_time": 165196.0,
      "text": "to examine an area called the retina."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 165196.0,
      "end_time": 168500.0,
      "text": "The retina is the single part of the eye that has"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 168500.0,
      "end_time": 170101.0,
      "text": "huge amounts of information about the body"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 170101.0,
      "end_time": 171889.0,
      "text": "and its health."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 171889.0,
      "end_time": 173700.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve developed 3D-printed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 173700.0,
      "end_time": 175141.0,
      "text": "low-cost hardware"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 175141.0,
      "end_time": 177541.0,
      "text": "that comes in at less than five dollars to produce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 177541.0,
      "end_time": 180484.0,
      "text": "which can then be clipped onto a smartphone"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 180484.0,
      "end_time": 181926.0,
      "text": "and makes it possible to get views"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 181926.0,
      "end_time": 183147.0,
      "text": "of the back of the eye"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 183147.0,
      "end_time": 184903.0,
      "text": "of a very high quality."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 184903.0,
      "end_time": 188100.0,
      "text": "And the beauty is, anybody can do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 188100.0,
      "end_time": 190978.0,
      "text": "In our trials on over two and half thousand people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 190979.0,
      "end_time": 192896.0,
      "text": "the smartphone with the add-on clip"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 192896.0,
      "end_time": 194577.0,
      "text": "is comparable to a camera"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 194577.0,
      "end_time": 196472.0,
      "text": "that is hugely more expensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 196472.0,
      "end_time": 200610.0,
      "text": "and hugely more difficult to transport."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 200610.0,
      "end_time": 201940.0,
      "text": "When we first moved to Kenya,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 201940.0,
      "end_time": 204593.0,
      "text": "we went with 150,000 dollars of equipment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 204593.0,
      "end_time": 207490.0,
      "text": "a team of 15 people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 207500.0,
      "end_time": 209942.0,
      "text": "and that was what was needed to deliver health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 209942.0,
      "end_time": 212307.0,
      "text": "Now, all that&#39;s needed"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 212307.0,
      "end_time": 214990.0,
      "text": "is a single person"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 214990.0,
      "end_time": 217494.0,
      "text": "on a bike with a smartphone."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 217495.0,
      "end_time": 221349.0,
      "text": "And it costs just 500 dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 221349.0,
      "end_time": 223219.0,
      "text": "The issue of power supply"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 223219.0,
      "end_time": 225780.0,
      "text": "is overcome by harnessing the power of solar."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 225780.0,
      "end_time": 226920.0,
      "text": "Our healthcare workers travel"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 226920.0,
      "end_time": 228464.0,
      "text": "with a solar-powered rucksack"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 228465.0,
      "end_time": 230926.0,
      "text": "which keeps the phone charged and backed up."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 230926.0,
      "end_time": 233196.0,
      "text": "Now we go to the patient"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 233196.0,
      "end_time": 235907.0,
      "text": "rather than waiting for the patient never to come."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 235907.0,
      "end_time": 237640.0,
      "text": "We go to them in their homes"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 237640.0,
      "end_time": 239436.0,
      "text": "and we give them the most comprehensive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 239437.0,
      "end_time": 241377.0,
      "text": "high-tech, accurate examination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 241377.0,
      "end_time": 245481.0,
      "text": "which can be delivered by anyone with minimal training."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 245481.0,
      "end_time": 248317.0,
      "text": "We can link global experts"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 248318.0,
      "end_time": 250600.0,
      "text": "with people in the most rural,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 250600.0,
      "end_time": 251250.0,
      "text": "difficult-to-reach places"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 251250.0,
      "end_time": 252839.0,
      "text": "that are beyond the end of the road,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 252839.0,
      "end_time": 255353.0,
      "text": "effectively putting those experts in their homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 255353.0,
      "end_time": 257331.0,
      "text": "allowing us to make diagnoses"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 257331.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260399.00000000003,
      "text": "and make plans for treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 260399.0,
      "end_time": 263126.0,
      "text": "Project managers, hospital directors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 263126.0,
      "end_time": 265440.0,
      "text": "are able to search on our interface"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 265450.0,
      "end_time": 267470.0,
      "text": "by any parameter they may be interested in."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 267470.0,
      "end_time": 269700.0,
      "text": "Here in Nakuru, where I&#39;ve been living,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 269700.0,
      "end_time": 270406.0,
      "text": "we can search for people"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 270406.0,
      "end_time": 271850.0,
      "text": "by whatever condition."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 271850.0,
      "end_time": 273122.0,
      "text": "Here are people who are blind"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 273122.0,
      "end_time": 275652.0,
      "text": "from a curable condition cataract."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 275652.0,
      "end_time": 277681.0,
      "text": "Each red pin depicts somebody"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 277681.0,
      "end_time": 280337.0,
      "text": "who is blind from a disease that is curable"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 280338.0,
      "end_time": 282584.0,
      "text": "and treatable, and they&#39;re locatable."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 282584.0,
      "end_time": 284468.0,
      "text": "We can use bulk text messaging services"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 284468.0,
      "end_time": 287622.0,
      "text": "to explain that we&#39;re coming to arrange a treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 287622.0,
      "end_time": 290237.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s more, we&#39;ve learned that this is something"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 290237.0,
      "end_time": 292275.0,
      "text": "that we haven&#39;t built just for the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 292275.0,
      "end_time": 293859.0,
      "text": "but with the community."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 293860.0,
      "end_time": 296112.0,
      "text": "Those blue pins that drop represent"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 296112.0,
      "end_time": 298213.0,
      "text": "elders, or local leaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 298213.0,
      "end_time": 299452.0,
      "text": "that are connected to those people"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 299452.0,
      "end_time": 300785.0,
      "text": "who can ensure that we can find them"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 300785.0,
      "end_time": 302886.0,
      "text": "and arrange treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 302886.0,
      "end_time": 305888.0,
      "text": "So for patients like Mama Wangari,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 305888.0,
      "end_time": 307484.0,
      "text": "who have been blind for over 10 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 307484.0,
      "end_time": 309113.0,
      "text": "and never seen her grandchildren,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 309113.0,
      "end_time": 312931.0,
      "text": "for less than 40 dollars, we can restore her eyesight."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 312931.0,
      "end_time": 318209.0,
      "text": "This is something that has to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 318209.0,
      "end_time": 319840.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s only in statistics"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 319840.0,
      "end_time": 322563.0,
      "text": "that people go blind by the millions."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 322563.0,
      "end_time": 326431.0,
      "text": "The reality is everyone goes blind on their own."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 326431.0,
      "end_time": 328407.0,
      "text": "But now, they might just be"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 328408.0,
      "end_time": 330547.0,
      "text": "a text message away from help."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 330547.0,
      "end_time": 336483.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 337295.0,
      "end_time": 339426.0,
      "text": "And now because live demos are always a bad idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 339426.0,
      "end_time": 341224.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to try a live demo."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 341224.0,
      "end_time": 342479.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 342480.0,
      "end_time": 347165.0,
      "text": "So here we have the Peek Vision app."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 352142.0,
      "end_time": 354786.0,
      "text": "Okay, and what we&#39;re looking at here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 354786.0,
      "end_time": 356281.0,
      "text": "this is Sam&#39;s optic nerve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 356281.0,
      "end_time": 358680.0,
      "text": "which is a direct extension of her brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 358680.0,
      "end_time": 361289.0,
      "text": "so I&#39;m actually looking at her brain as we look there."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 361289.0,
      "end_time": 364820.0,
      "text": "We can see all parts of the retina."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 364820.0,
      "end_time": 367349.0,
      "text": "It makes it possible to pick up diseases"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 367350.0,
      "end_time": 369517.0,
      "text": "of the eye and of the body"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 369517.0,
      "end_time": 372460.0,
      "text": "that would not be possible without access to the eye,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 372460.0,
      "end_time": 373981.0,
      "text": "and that clip-on device can be manufactured"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 373981.0,
      "end_time": 375531.0,
      "text": "for just a few dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 375531.0,
      "end_time": 377162.0,
      "text": "and people can be cured of blindness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 377162.0,
      "end_time": 380385.0,
      "text": "and I think it says a lot about us as a human race"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 380385.0,
      "end_time": 382909.0,
      "text": "if we&#39;ve developed cures and we don&#39;t deliver them."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 382910.0,
      "end_time": 384108.0,
      "text": "But now we can."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 384108.0,
      "end_time": 386324.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 386324.0,
      "end_time": 388488.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}